<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.2.6">
<l>mātarmā maṇmaṭan taiporuṭ ṭēṉamā</l>
<l>yātiyaṅ kālat takaliṭaṅ kīṇṭavar</l>
<l>pātaṅkaṇ mēlaṇi paimpoṟ ṟuḻāyeṉṟē</l>
<l>yōtummā leytiṉa ḷeṉṟaṉ maṭantaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“The fresh golden Tulsi [that is the] decoration on the feet</l>
<l>of him who tore the vast area at the primordial time,</l>
<l>becoming a boar for the sake of the beautiful dark earth girl”,</l>
<l>thus recites the girl of me who begot [her].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
